    "body": "Hey Paul,\r\n\r\nI think you are missing the [type extensions file](https://github.com/nomiclabs/buidler/tree/master/packages/buidler-ethers#typescript-support) from your `tsconfig.json`.\r\n\r\n`ethers` is not defined in `@nomiclabs/buidler`, but in the `@nomiclabs/buidler-ethers` plugin at runtime. When using TS, you need to let the compiler know about this. This is why you need the type extensions file.\r\n\r\nLet me know if this solves your problem.",
